Package: nfidd.forecasting
Title: Material to support course on forecasting and evaluation of infectious
    disease dynamics
Version: 1.2.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "NFIDD SISMID course contributors",
      family = "",
      role = c("cre", "aut"),
      email = "epiforecasts@gmail.com"
    )
  )
Description: Resources to support a short course on forecasting and evaluation
    of infectious disease dynamics, covering forecasting concepts and models,
    forecast evaluation, ensembles, and collaborative (hubverse) modelling.
